                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>2</p>\n            <p>is occurring among their friends abroad, than to read sermons<lb/> which they would\n                not go to a Synagogue to hear.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\"><persName>Mr Raphael's</persName> success has not been <add>?</add>\n                a <add>?</add><lb/> than was anticipated. Even in <placeName>England</placeName> he\n                was considered<lb/> a great man and his <add>?</add> there had established<lb/> his\n                name. I shall probably have an opportunity<lb/> of seeing him in <placeName>New\n                    York</placeName>. I may have <add>?</add>one before the<lb/> Arrival of the next\n                Occidents—which you had better<lb/> direct to <persName>A Joseph &amp;\n                    Co.</persName> and they will be <add>?</add> &amp;<lb/> distributed.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(8)\">Until I see you Believe me D. Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(9)\">Truly Yours</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">M Joseph</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p><sic>Tendere</sic> in Bills $14</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Rem 2%—28 16. 28 3. 11. 8</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4)\">11 due you.</p>"
                  },
